EU Says EBA Intends to Complete Bank Reassessment by Ecofin

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-14T10:50:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/eu-says-eba-intends-to-complete-bank-reassessment-by-ecofin.html
The European Banking Authority
intends to complete an assessment of the region’s capital needs
in time for a meeting of European Union finance ministers next
week, said  Jonathan Todd , a spokesman for the European
Commission.  “The EBA’s intention is to finalize their reassessment in
time for that” meeting, Todd told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
